          <li><strong>Priority-based filtering:</strong> Critical cases surface first - no need to scan every patient</li>
          <li><strong>Risk stratification:</strong> AI calculates risk scores so you don't have to manually assess each case</li>
          <li><strong>Smart alerts:</strong> Only high-priority patients require immediate action - low-risk cases stay on your radar but don't clutter the dashboard</li>
          <li><strong>Contextual information:</strong> Clinical notes and allergy details at a glance - no hunting through EMR tabs</li>
          <li><strong>Quick actions:</strong> One-click access to drug interaction checks and medication history</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  );
};

